{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"submit","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/submit_event","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>submit</code> 事件會在表單送出時觸發。</p>\n\n<p>要注意的是，<code>submit</code> 事件<strong>只會</strong>在 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\">form element</a> 上觸發， <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\">button</a> 或是 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\">submit input</a> 則不會觸發。（送出的是「表單」，而非「按鈕」）</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本資料","title":"基本資料","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"定義規範\">定義規範</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/association-of-controls-and-forms.html#form-submission-algorithm\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd>是 <br>\n 雖說在規範上這是個不 bubble 的事件</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd>是</dd>\n <dt id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n <dd>Element</dd>\n <dt id=\"默認行動\">默認行動</dt>\n <dd>修改（傳送表單內容至伺服器）。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-submit","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLFormElement.submit_event"}}],"toc":[{"text":"基本資料","id":"基本資料"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"}],"summary":"submit 事件會在表單送出時觸發。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"submit","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement: submit event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onsubmit","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"submit","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement: submit イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onsubmit","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement: submit event","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onsubmit","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement: submit event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/htmlformelement/submit_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blo